Customer Successes
Personalised experience¬

In-store sales associates have a direct line to the customer, with visibility into how customers respond to products, how merchandising is working, and the effectiveness of in-store promotions. Arm your sales associates, buyers, and store management with the information to quickly respond to customer needs and improve service.
The right products & services¬
Give customers a better experience and selection. Combine online and in-store transactional and behavioral data to predict what products customers would be most likely to purchase next.

Microsoft and our partners arm retailers and brands with solutions to help cost-effectively manage inventory and make sure the right products are in the right locations to optimise the customer experience through predictive analytics.
Visualise data¬

Unleash new value through connecting to data, services, and people outside your organisation, and deliver new insights for all users through familiar tools such as Office and SharePoint. Power BI for Office 365 is a powerful solution that enables every business professional, regardless of technical skills or experience with data analysis, to explore data and uncover important, meaningful insights and to share these with others quickly and easily.
